\f0\b\fs34 \cf2 \strokec2 1. Company & Tool Overview\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf2 Singulare
\f1\b0  is a B2B SaaS platform for medical clinics in Brazil. We provide a unified dashboard combining clinic operations (appointment management, patient communications via WhatsApp, electronic medical documents, automated patient review collection via NPS) and marketing intelligence (online presence score, social media post generation, search demand insights for the clinic's medical specialty within its city/region).\
Our typical user is a medical clinic owner or manager \'97 non-technical healthcare professional. We currently serve approximately 50\'96200 clinics, with steady growth.\
