\f0\b\fs34 \cf2 2. Purpose of Google Ads API Access\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 We will use 
\f0\b only
\f1\b0  the Keyword Plan Idea Service of the Google Ads API to provide aggregated, regional search-volume insights to our medical-clinic customers as part of a "Market Intelligence" feature in their dashboard.\
We are 
\f0\b not
\f1\b0  building an advertising campaign management tool. We will not create, modify, pause, resume, or report on Google Ads campaigns via the API.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

